    <lb n="26"/>πρὸς τὸ ἑκάτ<unclear>ερ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear>ν</unclear> ἔχειν μοναχόν. <supplied reason="omitted">καὶ</supplied> ἀλλή<unclear>λ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear>υ</unclear>ς <subst><add place="inline"><expan>ἐπερωτήσαντ<ex>ες</ex></expan></add><del rend="corrected">επερ<unclear>α</unclear>τησαντ</del></subst> ἀλλήλοις 

